quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,Mpe liboso tosilaki kopesa Ibrâhîm bokambi mpe biso nde toyebaki yango
  21,52,"Tango alobaki na tata waye mpe bato naye: Oyo bikeko nini bozali komipesa na yango"
  21,53,"Balobaki: Tokutaki batata na biso (to, bankoko na bango ya kala) bazalaki kobondela yango"
  21,54,"Alobi: Ya soló, bino na bango bozalaki na libunga ya polele"
  21,55,"Balobaki: Oyeli biso bosóló to ozali kosakana"
  21,56,"Alobi: Kasi Nkolo wa bino azali Nkolo wa likolo mpe nsé oyo akela yango, mpe ngai nazali moko kati ya banzeneneke na yango"
  21,57,"Mpe na lapi na Allah, ete nakani bikeko bia bino osima ya kokende na bino"
  21,58,"Abuki yango biteni biteni, atiki oyo ya monene, mpo tango mosusu bakozongela yango"
  21,59,"Balobi: Nani asali banzambe na biso boye? Ya soló, ye azali moko ya babubi"
  21,60,"Balobi: Bayebisi biso oyo asali boye ezali elenge mobali moko nkombo naye Ibrâhîm"
  21,61,"Balobi: Bomema ye awa na miso ya bato mpo bakoka kotatola"
  21,62,"Balobi: Yo nde osali boye na banzambe na biso oh Ibrâhîm"
  21,63,"Alobi: Oyo asali boye nde mokolo wa bango oyo, botuna bango soki bakoki koloba"
  21,64,"Bazongisaki mayele na bango mpe balobi: Ya sólo, bino nde bozali babubi"
  21,65,"Sima mabe ezongeli bango moko mpe balobi: Oyebi malamu ete (bikeko) oyo bilobaka te"
  21,66,"Alobi: Boye bozali kobondela na botiki Allah maye makosalisa bino te mpe makosala bino mabe te"
  21,67,"Ufi na bino na maye bozali kobondela biye bizali Allah te, boye bozali kokanisa te"
  21,68,"Balobi: Bozikisa ye, mpe bosunga banzambe na bino. Soki ya sólo, bolingi kosala"
  21,69,"Tolobaki: Eh móto! Zala malili mpe kimia тропа Ibrâhîm"
  21,70,"Mpe balingaki kosala ye mabe, kasi totiyaki bango o kati ya bazangi mpenza"
  21,71,"Mpe topesaki ye elonga, mpe Loth lokola, mpe totindaki bango o mboka eye to pambolaki yango mpo na bato ya mokili mobimba"
  21,72,"Mpe topesaki ye Is’háq na Ya’qúb ndenge asengaki, mpe banso totiyaki bango o kati ya bato malamu"
  21,73,"Mpe totiyaki bango bakambi, mpo bakamba na mibeko mia biso, mpe tolakisaki bango kosala bolamu, mpe kotelemisa losambo mpe kopesa zakat mpe bazalaki babondeli na biso"
  21,74,"Mpe topesaki Loth bwanya na boyebi, mpe tobikisaki ye na mboka oyo bazalaki kosala mabe. Ya soló, bazalaki bato mabe mpe bazangi"
  21,75,"Mpe tokotisaki ye na mawa та biso, ya sólo azali kati na bato ya malamu"